## ğŸ“Œ Project Overview

This project uses the **Maven Hospital Dataset** to analyze hospital operations, clinical activities, and financial performance. The dataset typically contains information related to patients, hospital visits, diagnoses, treatments, and billing.

This README provides a clear overview of the dataset structure, project setup, and possible analysis ideas.

