## ğŸ“Š Possible Analysis

Potential analysis ideas using this dataset:

* Patient admission and discharge trends
* Number of patients by department
* Most common diagnoses
* Average treatment cost
* Insurance vs out-of-pocket payment analysis
* Length of Stay (LOS) analysis

